'''-{zh-hans:雅各布·威廉·里斯-莫格;zh-hant:雅各·威廉·里斯-莫格;zh-hk:李思銘;}-'''（{{lang-en|Jacob William Rees-Mogg}}，{{bd|1969年|5月24日}}），[[英格蘭|英國]]政治人物，[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨成員]]，自2019年起於[[约翰逊内阁|约翰逊内阁]]擔任[[樞密院議長|樞密院議長]]、[[下議院領袖|下議院領袖]]。

里斯-莫格在[[2010年英國大選|2010年]]當選[[東北薩默塞特_(英國國會選區)|英格蘭薩默塞特東北選區]]的[[國會議員_(英國)|國會議員]]，連任至今。他是保守黨內的[[社会保守主义|社會保守主義者]]和[[歐洲懷疑主義|歐盟懷疑主義者]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/commons/mr-jacob-rees-mogg/4099 | title=Jacob Rees-Mogg | publisher=[[英国议会|英国议会]] | accessdate=2012-10-14 | archive-date=2015-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709153604/http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/commons/mr-jacob-rees-mogg/4099 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦是[[英國脫歐|英國脫離歐盟運動]]的重要推動者之一，曾任保守黨[[議會黨團|議會黨團]]{{le|欧洲研究小组|European Research Group}}主席。

== 早年生平 == 
=== 幼年與教育 ===
里斯-莫格在1969年5月24日生於[[英格兰|英格兰]][[漢默史密斯|漢默史密斯]]，父親是《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》前編輯{{le|威廉·里斯-莫格|William Rees-Mogg|威廉·里-{}-斯-莫格}}（1988年冊封為里-{}-斯-莫格勳爵），母親是保守黨籍{{le|聖潘克拉斯市長列表|List of mayors of St Pancras|聖潘克拉斯自治市市長}}托馬斯·理查德·莫里斯（{{lang|en|Thomas Richard Morris}}）之女芝莉安·莎士比亞·莫里斯（{{lang|en|Gillian Shakespeare Morris}}）。他有四名兄弟姊妹，三個比她年長，另有一個妹妹，即後來的[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]議員{{le|安农齐亚塔·里斯-莫格|Annunziata Rees-Mogg|-{安農齊亞塔·里斯-莫格}-}}。

他的家人在他出生前5年購買了[[森麻實郡|森麻實郡]]{{le|斯通伊斯頓|Ston Easton}}的一座[[英格蘭鄉村別墅|鄉村別墅]]——{{le|斯通伊斯頓莊園|Ston Easton Park}}，成為他成長的地方。他恆常參加每週的{{le|天主教會彌撒|Mass in the Catholic Church}}，偶爾在屬[[天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]的{{le|米德桑麻諾頓聖靈堂|Church of the Holy Ghost, Midsomer Norton}}上[[主日學|主日學]]<ref>{{Cite news |last=Teahan |first=Madeleine |date=2013-08-02 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: 'I think Mass can be too noisy and guitars should be banned' |work=[[The_Catholic_Herald|The Catholic Herald]] |url=http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/news/2013/08/02/jacob-rees-mogg-i-think-mass-can-be-too-noisy-and-guitars-should-be-banned/  |access-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906013930/http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/news/2013/08/02/jacob-rees-mogg-i-think-mass-can-be-too-noisy-and-guitars-should-be-banned/ |archive-date=2017-09-06}}</ref>。1975年起，他與[[女家庭教師|女家庭教師]]進行[[教义问答|教义问答]]和開始{{le|保祿六世彌撒|Mass of Paul VI|一般彌撒}}<ref>{{Cite news |last=Teahan |first=Madeleine |date=2017-02-02 |title=PODCAST: Jacob Rees-Mogg goes on retreat |work=[[The_Catholic_Herald|The Catholic Herald]] |url=http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/commentandblogs/2017/02/02/podcast-jacob-rees-mogg-goes-on-retreat/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904201914/http://www.catholicherald.co.uk/commentandblogs/2017/02/02/podcast-jacob-rees-mogg-goes-on-retreat/ |archive-date=2017-09-04}}</ref>。1978年，他舉家遷到鄰近的村莊{{le|欣頓布萊維特|Hinton Blewett}}，他們購置了「舊教區長府邸」（{{lang|en|The Old Rectory}}），以前為教區長住所，如今是市值2百萬英鎊的[[登錄建築|二級登錄建築]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=Steeples |first=Matthew |date=2016-10-24 |title=The House of Mogg |url=http://thesteepletimes.com/opulence-splendour/the-house-of-mogg/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201020110/http://thesteepletimes.com/opulence-splendour/the-house-of-mogg/ |archive-date=2018-02-01 |access-date=2017-01-31 |website=The Steeple Times}}</ref>。他雖然居住在森麻實郡，但因為要到[[獨立學校_(英國)|私立]]{{le|預備學校 (英國)|Preparatory school (United Kingdom)|預備學校}}{{le|西敏小學|Westminster Under School}}上學，而經常往返[[伦敦|伦敦]][[史密斯广场|史密斯广场]]的家族住宅<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |last=Wilson |first=Rob |date=2012-07-09 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: a Boris in the making? |url=https://www.totalpolitics.com/articles/interview/jacob-rees-mogg-boris-making |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904201115/https://www.totalpolitics.com/articles/interview/jacob-rees-mogg-boris-making |archive-date=2017-09-04 |access-date=2017-09-02 |website=[[Total_Politics|Total Politics]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The polite extremist: Jacob Rees-Mogg's seemingly unstoppable rise |url=https://www.newstatesman.com/politics/uk/2018/02/polite-extremist-jacob-rees-mogg-s-seemingly-unstoppable-rise?page=46 |access-date=2018-05-30 |website=www.newstatesman.com}}</ref>。

兒時的里斯-莫格由[[褓姆|褓姆]]維朗妮卡·克魯克（{{Lang|en|Veronica Crook}}）照顧，里斯-莫格形容對方是「影響他成長的人」，現時克魯克已侍奉其家族逾50年，仍然在照料里斯-莫格自己的兒女<ref>{{Cite news |last=Rees-Mogg |first=Jacob |date=2014-03-14 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: My nanny made me the man I am |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/10698217/Jacob-Rees-Mogg-My-nanny-made-me-the-man-I-am.html |access-date=2017-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319002758/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/10698217/Jacob-Rees-Mogg-My-nanny-made-me-the-man-I-am.html |archive-date=2017-03-19}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web |last=Horton |first=Helena |date=2017-07-21 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: I have six children but have never changed a nappy |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/07/21/jacob-rees-mogg-have-six-children-have-never-changed-nappy/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908004756/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/07/21/jacob-rees-mogg-have-six-children-have-never-changed-nappy/ |archive-date=2017-09-08 |access-date=2017-09-09 |website=The Telegraph}}</ref>。

當里斯-莫格10歲時，一名遠房表親送了10英鎊給他，父親替他買了現時已結業的[[英國通用電氣公司|英國通用電氣公司]]股份。後來他認為，這是他對股票市場產生興趣的原因。當他明白公司的財務報告後，他在英國通用電氣公司的一場股東會議上反對了一項議案，理由是股東分紅太低<ref name="Oldroyd-Bolt">{{Cite news |last=Oldroyd-Bolt |first=David |date=2016-11-03 |title=The many, many millions of Mogg |work=Spectator Life |location=London |url=https://life.spectator.co.uk/2016/11/many-many-millions-mogg/ |access-date=2017-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904204458/https://life.spectator.co.uk/2016/11/many-many-millions-mogg/ |archive-date=2017-09-04}}</ref>。他其後又投資基地位於倫敦的[[綜合企業|綜合企業]]「{{le|Lonrho|Lonrho}}」，前後累積持340股，在[[股东大会|股东大会]]質問有關股東紅利的問題，據報令時任公司主席[[邓肯·桑兹|鄧肯-桑茲勳爵]]有些「不舒服」。1981年，當時12歲的里斯-莫格持有175股，他在股東會議上告訴時任公司主席{{le|第二代斯塔福德的納爾遜男爵·亨利|Henry Nelson, 2nd Baron Nelson of Stafford|納爾遜勳爵}}，現在提議的股東紅利是「令人悲哀」，惹來在場的公司董事和傳媒忍俊不禁<ref>{{Cite news |last=Woods |first=Vicki |date=1985 |title=Ever wondered what Jacob Rees-Mogg was like as a teenager? |work=[[Tatler|Tatler]] |url=http://www.tatler.com/article/jacob-rees-mogg-interview |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904204054/http://www.tatler.com/article/jacob-rees-mogg-interview |archive-date=2017-09-04}}</ref>。

上完預備學校後，他進入了[[伊顿公学|伊顿公学]]，曾在一份功課中被評價為「相當自以為是的[[撒切尔主义|戴卓爾主義者]]」<ref>{{Cite web |last=Wilson |first=Rob |date=2012-07-09 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: a Boris in the making? |url=https://www.totalpolitics.com/articles/interview/jacob-rees-mogg-boris-making |access-date=2019-03-12 |website=totalpolitics.com |publisher=Dods Group plc}}</ref>。準備離開伊頓之際，{{le|皇家肖像畫師學會|Royal Society of Portrait Painters}}會員保羅·布蘭森（{{lang|en|Paul Branson}}）為他作畫給予{{le|伊頓公學收藏品系列|Eton College Collections}}，其肖像畫於皇家肖像畫師學會畫展《1993年的臉孔》上被展出<ref>{{Cite news |date=1993-05-11 |title=Faces of 1993 go on show at Royal Society of Portrait Painters' annual exhibition |work=The Telegraph |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/faces-of-1993-go-on-show-at-royal-society-of-portrait-painters-annual-exhibition-2322303.html |access-date=2017-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904202338/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/faces-of-1993-go-on-show-at-royal-society-of-portrait-painters-annual-exhibition-2322303.html |archive-date=2017-09-04}}</ref>。

里斯-莫格在[[牛津大学三一学院|牛津大学三一学院]]攻讀歷史，於1991年畢業並取得{{le|英國本科學位分類|British undergraduate degree classification|二級甲等榮譽}}<ref name="Adams2">{{Cite news |last=Adams |first=Guy |date=2006-10-19 |title=Rees-Mogg: First family of fogeys |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/reesmogg-first-family-of-fogeys-420663.html |access-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141119204854/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/reesmogg-first-family-of-fogeys-420663.html |archive-date=2014-11-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Vote 2001 – Candidate: Jacob Rees-Mogg |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/vote2001/candidates/candidates/2/25304.stm |access-date=2017-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040512211559/http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/vote2001/candidates/candidates/2/25304.stm |archive-date=2004-05-12}}</ref>。1988年剛入學時，牛津大學學生報《{{Lang|en|Cherwell}}》已經稱他是「咄咄逼人的新生」，刊出一幅里斯-莫格身穿西裝的照片，寫道「我們還有什麼要說？」<ref name="kuper20190620">{{Cite news |last=Kuper |first=Simon |date=2019-06-20 |title=How Oxford university shaped Brexit — and Britain's next prime minister |work=Financial Times |url=https://www.ft.com/content/85fc694c-9222-11e9-b7ea-60e35ef678d2 |access-date=2019-06-21}}</ref>。在牛津就讀時，他曾是{{le|牛津大學保守黨協會|Oxford University Conservative Association}}的主席，《{{Lang|en|Cherwell}}》形容為提倡「征服世界和社會適足性的競選活動」。他同時亦是[[牛津大學辯論社|牛津大學辯論社]]的會員，經常參與辯論，選舉社團幹事時他當選圖書館館員，但[[達米安·海因斯|達米安·海因斯]]擊敗他當選主席<ref>{{Cite news |last=Dennis |first=Charlie |date=2013-10-21 |title=This House believes that the EU is a threat to democracy |work=Oxford Student |url=http://oxfordstudent.com/2013/10/31/this-house-believes-that-the-eu-is-a-threat-to-democracy/ |access-date=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601003803/http://oxfordstudent.com/2013/10/31/this-house-believes-that-the-eu-is-a-threat-to-democracy/ |archive-date=2015-06-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Fraser |first=Rory |date=2015-11-02 |title=Interview: Jacob-Rees Mogg |work=Cherwell |url=http://www.cherwell.org/2015/11/02/interview-jacobrees-mogg/ |access-date=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720150739/http://www.cherwell.org/2015/11/02/interview-jacobrees-mogg/ |archive-date=2017-07-20}}</ref>{{r|kuper20190620}}。他回憶大學生活時，曾言後悔沒研讀[[古典學|古典學]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=Lange-Kuettner |first=Chris |date=2017-08-13 |title=Interview with The Mogg |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/rees-mogg-an-english-trump-but-better-at-latin-mdm82q87j |access-date=2017-09-01 |website=The Times}}</ref>。

=== 職業生涯 ===
1991年從牛津畢業後，里斯-莫格到{{le|羅斯柴爾德公司|Rothschild & Co|羅斯柴爾德投資銀行}}跟從{{le|尼爾斯·塔布|Nils Taube}}工作，其後於1993年轉到[[香港|香港]]於「羅祖儒投資管理有限公司」（Lloyd George Management）供職<ref name=":2">{{Cite news |last=Livsey |first=Alan |date=2017-10-16 |title=Brexiter Jacob Rees-Mogg's lacklustre record as a fund manager |work=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]] |url=https://www.ft.com/content/d9f42362-aea0-11e7-beba-5521c713abf4 |access-date=2017-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021220754/https://www.ft.com/content/d9f42362-aea0-11e7-beba-5521c713abf4 |archive-date=2017-10-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Cumming |first=Shaun |title=Jet-set team on the hunt for income |work=Fund Strategy |publisher=[[Centaur_Media|Centaur Media]] |url=http://www.fundweb.co.uk/fund-strategy/issues/9-january-2012/jet-set-team-on-the-hunt-for-income/1043942.article |access-date=2013-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907142838/http://www.fundweb.co.uk/fund-strategy/issues/9-january-2012/jet-set-team-on-the-hunt-for-income/1043942.article |archive-date=2014-09-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Mason |first=Rowena |date=2017-08-14 |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg: the Brexit-loving right's answer to Corbyn? |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/aug/14/jacob-rees-mogg-the-brexit-loving-rights-answer-to-corbyn |access-date=2017-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902005656/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/aug/14/jacob-rees-mogg-the-brexit-loving-rights-answer-to-corbyn |archive-date=2017-09-02}}</ref>。據說他留港期間成為了[[香港總督|總督]][[彭定康|彭定康]]的好友，並經常到訪[[香港禮賓府|總督府]]。三年後，他返回倫敦，被調派掌管公司的新興市場基金。2003年左右，他開始負責管理「羅祖儒新興市場基金公司」<ref>{{Cite web |date=2003-01-02 |title=Rees-Mogg to run Lloyd George emerging fund |url=https://www.professionaladviser.com/international-investment/news/1329428/rees-mogg-run-lloyd-george-emerging-fund |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204161611/https://www.professionaladviser.com/international-investment/news/1329428/rees-mogg-run-lloyd-george-emerging-fund |archive-date=2018-02-04 |access-date=2017-10-21 |website=Professional Adviser}}</ref>。2007年，里斯-莫格連同一些同事離開了「羅祖儒公司」，並一同開展了他們的新公司「森麻實資本管理有限公司」，獲空頭對衝基金經理{{le|克里斯平·奧迪|Crispin Odey}}支持<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg |url=http://www.trustnet.com/Managers/ManagerFactsheet.aspx?personCode=00000MOG01&univ=O |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129041814/http://www.trustnet.com/Managers/ManagerFactsheet.aspx?personCode=00000MOG01&univ=O |archive-date=2014-11-29 |access-date=2013-01-15 |publisher=Trustnet}}</ref>。隨著他2010年選舉中勝出並當選為[[東北薩默塞特_(英國國會選區)|東北薩默塞特選區]]的[[國會議員_(英國)|國會議員]]，他便辭任「森麻實資本管理有限公司」行政總裁一職，但仍繼續以合夥人身份領取公司收入<ref name=":2" />。

== 投身政治 ==
=== 國會議員候選人 ===
1997年，時為27歲的里斯-莫格首次參與政治，在[[1997年英國大選|1997年英國大選]]為[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]參選位於蘇格蘭的傳統[[工党_(英国)|工黨]]議席{{le|中法夫 (英國國會選區)|Central Fife (UK Parliament constituency)|中法夫}}。[[上流社會|上流社會背景]]的他在選民主要是[[工人阶级|工人阶级]]的選區十分不討好，經常被批評過於「高檔」<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Prime Minister for the 18th Century - Platinum Publishing Group |url=https://www.platinumpublishing.co.uk/platinum-business-magazine/2018/10/the-prime-minister-for-the-18th-century/ |access-date=2020-08-09 |website=www.platinumpublishing.co.uk |language=en}}</ref>。當時的新聞報導揶揄他乘著賓利，攜同他的保姆在選舉拉票。他後來批評報章誹謗，澄清那是台[[梅賽德斯－賓士|梅賽德斯]]<ref>{{Cite news |last=Woods |first=Judith |date=2013-06-18 |title=I will never be a phoney man of the people |work=The Daily Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/features/10125164/I-will-never-be-a-phoney-man-of-the-people.html |access-date=2013-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130910055907/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/features/10125164/I-will-never-be-a-phoney-man-of-the-people.html |archive-date=2013-09-10}}</ref><ref name="Adams2" />。里斯-莫格最後僅得票9%排第三，比起前數任保守黨參選人低不少，而認得他名字的選民甚至不足2%<ref>{{Cite news |last=Fraser |first=Douglas |date=1997-04-17 |title=Election '97 : Old Etonian finds Fife a school of hard knocks |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/election-97-old-etonian-finds-fife-a-school-of-hard-knocks-1267755.html |access-date=2017-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905184044/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/election-97-old-etonian-finds-fife-a-school-of-hard-knocks-1267755.html |archive-date=2017-09-05}}</ref>。

1999年，當有傳聞指其「不合時宜地高檔」的口音令他不獲挑選為保守黨的安全議席參選，不少讀者寫信至《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》為里斯-莫格辯護，有一名更稱「現時有一股公然的恫嚇存在，朝著那些敢於不迎合現時[[美國化|美國化]]的行為、言談和衣著」<ref name="Mullen">{{Cite news |last=Mullen |first=John |date=1999-06-18 |title=Lost voices |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/1999/jun/18/features11.g22 |access-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508034936/http://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/1999/jun/18/features11.g22 |archive-date=2014-05-08}}</ref>。里斯-莫格本人亦在1999年5月23日的《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士報]]》說「為口音而大驚小怪真的可悲」，但他在同一篇報道卻稱「[[彭仕國|彭仕國]]的口音毫無疑問會令人建立他是個粗人的成見」<ref name="Mullen" />；他之後為此言論道歉並表示後悔<ref>[[BBC_One|BBC One]] (20 November 2015). ''[[Have_I_Got_A_Bit_More_News_For_You|Have I Got A Bit More News For You]]''. S50E07. Rees-Mogg: "... if Lord Prescott is watching, may I apologise ... because I think it was a rude thing to have said and I regret having said that."</ref>，他亦說道：「我漸漸開始發現，不論我想要說什麼，我支持者的數量都會隨著我張開口而下降。」<ref name="Jack">{{Cite news |last=Jack |first=Ian |author-link=Ian Jack |date=2010-04-24 |title=In pursuit of Somerset royalty in the hyper-marginal hinterland |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2010/apr/24/somerset-jacob-rees-mogg-conservatives |access-date=2013-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194852/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2010/apr/24/somerset-jacob-rees-mogg-conservatives |archive-date=2013-10-29}}</ref>

里斯-莫格於[[2001年英國大選|2001年英國大選]]再次被選為保守黨國會議員參選人，這次是[[什罗普郡|什罗普郡]]的[[里金_(英國國會選區)|里金選區]]，但敗給了當時競逐連任的[[國會議員_(英國)|國會議員]]<ref>{{Cite news |title=Election 2010: The Wrekin |work=[[Shropshire_Star|Shropshire Star]] |url=http://www.shropshirestar.com/election-2010-telford/election-2010-the-wrekin/ |access-date=2013-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001222335/http://www.shropshirestar.com/election-2010-telford/election-2010-the-wrekin/ |archive-date=2013-10-01}}</ref>。2005年至2008年，他被推選為倫敦及西敏市{{le|保守黨協會|Conservative Association}}的主席。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Jacob Rees-Mogg MP |work=BBC News |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/42117.stm |access-date=2013-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130307232153/http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/42117.stm |archive-date=2013-03-07}}</ref>

